{"tid":2376881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息：（23/1）新增約80宗確診個案，累計個案料破萬宗","createTime":"2021-01-23T06:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T07:32:31.000Z","uid":278587,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"28c897bf587535365031f073d7904af9166318aa","tid":2376881,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2860000/2860652/cases_thumb_20210123_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2860000%2F2860652%2Fcases_thumb_20210123_S_1024.jpg&h=8424d8cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情持續，其中油尖旺區確診持續，今日是抗疫一周年，去年今日本港錄得首宗輸入確診病例，消息指今日（23日）新增約80宗確診個案，確診數字又再度回升，累計個案料破萬宗。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署衞生防護中心昨日61宗新增確診個案，至今本港個案累計9,929宗，包括9,928宗確診個案和一宗疑似個案），昨日新增的個案中6宗為輸入個案。<br />\n<br />\n政府今日清晨圍封佐敦「受限區域」，東至吳松街、南至南京街、西至炮台街、北至甘肅街，範圍內的人士須留在處所，並按政府安排接受強制檢測，未有檢測結果不可以離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2860652/【抗疫一周年】消息：新增約80宗確診個案%20%20%20累計個案料破萬宗?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2860652%2F%E3%80%90%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%91%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E7%B4%8480%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%2520%2520%2520%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E6%96%99%E7%A0%B4%E8%90%AC%E5%AE%97%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5IR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=721e9d23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2860652/【抗疫一周年】消息：新增約80宗確診個案%20%20%20累計個案料破萬宗?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"faa55fe2adee6c08fa009bfb2cd367f8dc674323","tid":2376881,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"